        <updateDate>2021-05-10T11:12:57Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>No Money Bail Act of 2021 </b> <p>This bill restricts the use of money bail (i.e., the payment of money as a condition of pretrial release) in criminal cases. <p>Specifically, it prohibits the use of money bail in federal criminal cases. <p>Additionally, it makes a state that uses a money bail system ineligible for funds under the Edward Byrne Memorial Justice Assistance Grant Program.]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
